Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:24.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們看戲  看厭了虛偽的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:24.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We've become bored with watching actors give us phony emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:28.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,看厭了花巧的特技
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:28.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We're tired of pyrotechnics and special effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:31.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門的世界...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:31.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,While the world he inhabits...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:34.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,可以說是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:34.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Is, in some respects, counterfeit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門本人卻半點不假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,There's nothing fake about Truman himself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:41.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,這節目沒有劇本  沒有提場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:41.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,No scripts   No cue cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:44.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,未必是傑作  但如假包換
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:44.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It isn't always Shakespeare, but it's genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:47.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,是一個人一生的真實記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:47.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:52.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我捱不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:52.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:56.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己去吧  不要等我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:56.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're going to have to go on without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.30,0:01:03.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,老兄  怎可以?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.30,0:01:03.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,No way, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:05.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你即使一拐一拐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:05.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're going to the top of this mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:07.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,也得爬上山頂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:07.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,broken legs and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:15.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,觀眾通宵收看  視他如良友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:15.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We find many viewers leave him on all night for comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:18.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你發神經  知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:18.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're crazy, You know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:26.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我的生活不分公私
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:26.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, for me, There is no difference between a private life and a public life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.80,0:01:29.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,"真人表演"是我全部的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.80,0:01:29.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,My life...is my life, is the Truman show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.10,0:01:32.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,"真人表演"是典範的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.10,0:01:32.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The Truman show Is...A lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:34.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,是高尚的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:34.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a noble life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:39.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,美滿的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:39.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It is...a truly blessed life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:42.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有什麼不知道  你說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:42.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, tell me something I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:45.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,好  你要答應我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:45.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,All right. Promise me one thing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:49.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,如果未到達山頂  而我死去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:49.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,If I die before I reach the summit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:53.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你要把我當作糧食
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:53.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You'll use me as an alternative source of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:55.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:55.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Ew. Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:02.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,內容真真實實  原原本本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:02.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's all true. It's all real.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:05.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,各位所見的  絕無虛假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:05.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Nothing here is fake. Nothing you see on this show is fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:07.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,有的只是調控
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:07.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's merely controlled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:18.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉我  我命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:18.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Eat me, damn it. That's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,也許只吃你喜歡的肚腩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe just your love handles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:25.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我有肚腩?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:25.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I have love handles?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:28.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,有  小肚腩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:28.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. Little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:31.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門  你快遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:31.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman, You're going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:50.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:48.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:50.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Morning. Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:51.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,假如再碰不見你們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:51.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, and in case I don't see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你早 午 晚都安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, Good evening, And good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 早安  楚門  - 早安  史賓沙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Morning.  - Morning, spencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,阿冥  不准
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, Pluto.No, no, no. Get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:01.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,阿冥不會咬你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:01.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He won't hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:05.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  但仍然怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:05.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Get down. Ha ha. I know.It's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:07.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,來  阿冥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:07.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on, Pluto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:11.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:11.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Ohh
