Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:20.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Holy cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:32.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:32.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,現在新聞簡報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Here's a news flash just in.
