Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,An aircraft in trouble began shedding parts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,發生故障  零件脫落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,As it flew over Seahaven just a few moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好沒有擊中人  各位可好?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Wow. Luckily, No one was hurt. But, hey, How do you feel today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,正打算搭飛機?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You thinking of flying somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不  - 不? 那就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Nope. - No? Good.
