Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Dog fancy, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:28.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,老嶽  一份報紙  還有...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:28.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Ahh! Give me a paper there, will you, earl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:32.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我要一本  太太愛看時裝雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:32.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, and, uh... One of these for the wife. Loves her fashion mags.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:35.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 還要什麼? 楚門  - 統統齊全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:35.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Will that be all for you, Truman?  - That's the whole kit and caboodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Catch you later. Ok.
