Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:48.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey. Hank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  楚門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Morning, Truman.
