Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:53.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Good morning, Truman. - Hey, how are you, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 今天天氣很好 是嗎?  - 天天都這樣好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Beautiful day, Isn't it?  - Oh. Always.
