Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You, too. Fine, fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:06.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要趕時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:06.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We must go now.
