Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:52.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Lawrence. - Hey, Burbank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:55.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,維園有一宗保險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:55.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Got a prospect in Wells Park
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你去成交
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I need you to close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:00.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,維園?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:00.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Wells park?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:04.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,在港島那裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:04.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,On, uh...Harbor Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,還有別處嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You know another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:11.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我要見牙醫  我的牙齒要補
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:11.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I, uh, have an appointment. Dentist. Or... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:15.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你賣不夠保險 要補的不僅是牙齒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:15.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're going to lose a lot more than your teeth if you don't meet your quota.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:20.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,公司打算月底裁員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:20.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,They're making cutbacks at the end of this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,裁員?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Cutbacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,這宗生意你一定要做成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. Now, you need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:27.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,順便去吹吹海風  對你有益
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:27.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Besides, a half hour across the bay, a little sea air...Would do you good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:42.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,渡輪還沒開出?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:42.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello. Ferry still here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為錯過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Thought I might have missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,單程還是來回?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,One-way or return?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:49.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,來回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:49.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你的票
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,There you go, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,可以幫你嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you need any help, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:55.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管我了  我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:55.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You go ahead. I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:12.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:12.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:16.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,超級市場有贈品  看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:16.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,look what I got free at the checkout.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,叫"廚師良伴"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a chef's pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,剁 磨 削  一物多用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a dicer, grater, peeler all in one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不會鈍  可以用洗碗碟機洗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Never needs sharpening, Dishwasher safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,真神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Wow. That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:30.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:30.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,剪漏了一塊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You missed a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,老天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,爽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:49.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,這才算是啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:49.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That is a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,馬龍  我想離開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You know, I'm thinking about getting out, Marlon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,離開? 離開什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah? Out of what? off this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:10:00.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,離開我的工作  離開桃源島
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:10:00.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Out of my job, Out of Seahaven. off this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:02.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你想辭工? 為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:02.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Out. Out of your job? What the hell's wrong with your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:06.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你的工作舒舒服服 只處理文件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:06.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You have a great job, Truman. You have a desk job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我很羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'd kill for a desk job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:12.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,到你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:12.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,想改行做雜貨?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You should try stocking vending machines for a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:16.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不想 - 雜貨夠刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:16.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- No, thanks. - Now, there's excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你從沒興趣到外面走走?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't you ever get antsy? Itchy feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:23.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,走到哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:23.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Where's there to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,菲濟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Fiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:31.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,菲濟在哪裡? 近佛羅里達?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:31.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Where the hell's Fiji? Near Florida?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:37.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,看見嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:37.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,See here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. This is us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,繞個圈...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And all the way around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,菲濟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Fiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:49.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,再走遠一點  就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:49.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You can't get any further away before you start coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:55.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,菲濟有些島嶼是沒有人到過的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:55.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You know, there are still islands in Fiji where no human being has ever set foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:00.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  你打算幾時去?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:00.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,So, when are you going to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,要去  並不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:10.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,需要錢 籌備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:10.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It takes...money, planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:13.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不能說走就走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:13.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't just up and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:14.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:14.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:18.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,但我會去  一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:18.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm going to do it. Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:21.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,公司很快派花紅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:21.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Bonus time is just around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:27.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,來喝杯酒嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:27.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, you coming for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:29.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:29.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,No. I can't tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:52.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎快有風暴  劃回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:52.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't like the look of that weather, son. I think we should head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:55.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 爸  多劃一會  - 應該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:55.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Oh, no, dad. Not yet. - No, come on. We should go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,多劃一會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,A bit farther. Listen...Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,爸!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:21.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,像只落湯雞  去過哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:21.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're soaked. Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,如果籌到八千元...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I figure if we can scrape together 8,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:27.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 每次跟馬龍玩完後... - 就能夠到處旅行一年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:27.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Every time you and Marlon get together... - We can bum around the world for a year on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:31.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,然後打回原形  不名一文
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:31.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And then what, Truman? We'd be where we were 5 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你不現實得像個少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're talking like a teenager.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,也許我的心境像少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, maybe I feel like a teenager.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:39.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要供房子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:39.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We have mortgage payments, Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:43.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,又要供車  怎丟得下?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:43.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We have car payments. What, we're just going to walk away from our financial obligations?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,會好刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It would be an adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不打算生兒育女嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought we were going to try for a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:51.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,還不夠刺激?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:51.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Isn't that enough of an adventure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,兒女可遲點生  我想出外走走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That can wait. I want to get away
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:57.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,見見世面  闖新天地!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:57.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,See some of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:59.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要成為探險家嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:59.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Honey, you want to be an explorer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:03.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,這種衝動誰都有過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:03.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,This'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:06.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,但遲早會明白不切實際
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:06.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We all think like this now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,先脫掉濕衫褲  好不好?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's get you out of these wet clothes, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:13.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,上床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:13.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Come to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:17.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你是看不到滴  每逢上床的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:17.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You never see anything anyway. They always...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:21.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,鏡頭必定移開  播放音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:21.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Turn the camera and play music and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:26.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,風吹簾動  觀眾什麼都看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:26.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You know, the wind blows in, and the curtains move, and you don't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- "狗迷"  麻煩你  - 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Dog fancy, please. - Dog fancy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:35.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:35.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:39.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,老嶽  報紙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:39.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Paper, Earl, please. Paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,順便要份時裝雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh...I might as well pick one of these up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 給太太的  - 少不得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- for the wife?  - She's got to have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 還要什麼? - 統統齊全
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Anything else, Truman? - That's the whole ball of wax.
