Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:15.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:20.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:20.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Ohh! Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:21.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:21.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey! What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:24.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:24.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:25.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,截停他們!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:25.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,截停他們!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop those people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:31.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,停!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:31.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:36.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,打開門! 停車!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:36.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey! Open the doors! Somebody stop the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:38.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,停下巴士!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:38.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:42.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,誰來幫忙停下它!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:40.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Somebody stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:42.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Somebody stop the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,停下巴士!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:07.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,一點也不出奇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:07.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It doesn't sound insane at all, Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:11.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我經常見到你爸爸的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:11.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I see him 10 times a week in a hundred different faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:15.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,上星期四  我差點抱錯了人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:15.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I almost hugged a perfect stranger in the salon last thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明見到爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It was dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他樣子像個流浪漢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I swear. Dressed like a homeless man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道最不可思議的是什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And you know what else Was strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:26.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,一個商人和一個拉著狗的女人 突然出現  把他推上巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:26.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,A businessman and a woman with a little dog came out of nowhere and forced him onto a bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:29.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,市政局早應該驅逐流浪漢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:29.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, it's about time they cleaned up the trash downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:31.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,否則本地也會亂七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:31.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Before we become just like the rest of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:34.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的屍體一直打撈不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:34.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,They never found Dad's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:34.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 或者...  - 別亂想了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:34.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Maybe somehow... - Oh, god.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:38.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我見到的難道是他的孿生兄弟?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:38.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, if it wasn't him, it was his twin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸有沒有兄弟?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Did dad have a brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:47.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你很清楚爸爸是個獨子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:47.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman, you know perfectly well. That your father was an only child
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:49.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,像你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:49.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:58.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門... 你爸爸淹死  你覺得內疚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:58.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, sweetie... You're just feeling bad because of what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你把船向風暴駛去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You sailing off into that storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:06.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,但我從來沒有怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:06.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,But I've never blamed you, Truman...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,一向都不怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And I don't blame you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:03.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你在地下室幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:03.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you doing down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:06.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,修理剪草機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:06.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Fixing the mower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我見到爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Saw my father today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:17.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你媽媽打過電話來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:17.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Your mother called.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:22.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你不應該觸動她的傷心事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:22.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You really shouldn't upset her like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:24.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,找我幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:24.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Did you want... What did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我煮了通心粉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I made macaroni.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我不餓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:34.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們應該扔掉那剪草機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:34.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You know...You really ought to throw out that mower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:37.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,買一部愛奇牌剪草機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:37.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Get one of those new Elk rotaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他在幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:18.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,她雖然被帶走 但他對她念念不忘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:18.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,See, they got rid of her, but they couldn't erase the memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不忘誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The memory of who?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:28.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,(桃源學院)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:28.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,[trumpet playing]
