Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:32.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- I'm Meryl. - Hi. I'm Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:34.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,幸會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:34.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:01.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門  你太用功了\N楚門  你太用功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:01.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman, you've studied enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:03.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我要記熟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:03.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,No. I got to commit this to memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:05.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去喝杯冰凍啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:05.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on, Truman, one ice-cold brewski.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:07.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:07.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.50,0:22:10.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你要小心  你抄我 我錯你就錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.50,0:22:10.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on. You're going to have to copy off me, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:12.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:12.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:16.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門  你比我老實  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:16.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,No? You're a better person than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:17.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:17.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.80,0:22:18.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.80,0:22:18.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Ok. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:20.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,再見  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:20.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Bye. See you later, loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:28.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好（日語）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:28.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Konnichi-wa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.50,0:23:30.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.50,0:23:30.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:33.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你在學日文
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:33.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh. You take japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:35.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:35.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:40.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫羅蘭  對嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:40.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Lauren, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.20,0:23:42.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,上面寫著...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.20,0:23:42.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's on the...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:45.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,羅蘭  對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:45.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Lauren. Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.60,0:23:48.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫楚門
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.60,0:23:48.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm Truman Burbank.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:51.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:51.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah...I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.30,0:23:54.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他們不准我跟你交談
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.30,0:23:54.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You know, I'm not allowed to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.30,0:23:55.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.30,0:23:55.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.40,0:24:02.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,可以明白  我是個危險人物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.40,0:24:02.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. Well, I can understand that. I'm a pretty dangerous character.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.20,0:24:04.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  我作不了主
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.20,0:24:04.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It's not up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.20,0:24:07.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,女兒家當然要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.20,0:24:07.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,A girl's got to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.00,0:24:11.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你有男朋友  對不對?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.00,0:24:11.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You have a boyfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.00,0:24:13.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因為男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.00,0:24:13.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.40,0:24:15.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,因為跟我一起那小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.40,0:24:15.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Was it Meryl, that girl that was with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.70,0:24:19.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們... 只是普通朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.70,0:24:19.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We're not...we don't...we're not...we're just...we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.30,0:24:20.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因為她
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.30,0:24:20.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.60,0:24:23.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我的樣子不合眼緣?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.60,0:24:23.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's how I look? Not your type?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:25.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:25.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.50,0:24:28.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你的襟章
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.50,0:24:28.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I like your pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.60,0:24:31.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.60,0:24:31.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I was wondering that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.50,0:24:35.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你願不願意... 可能的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.50,0:24:35.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Mmm. Would you want to...Maybe possibly...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.70,0:24:40.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,陪我上街  去吃薄餅?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.70,0:24:40.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Sometime go out for some pizza or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.40,0:24:41.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,星期五?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.40,0:24:41.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Like, friday?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.10,0:24:44.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 星期六?  - 我不能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.10,0:24:44.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Saturday?  - I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.50,0:24:46.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,星期日? 星期一? 星期二?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.50,0:24:46.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Sunday? Monday? Tuesday?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.70,0:24:52.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是期終考試
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.70,0:24:52.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We have finals tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.50,0:24:53.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.50,0:24:53.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.00,0:24:57.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在不去  以後沒有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.00,0:24:57.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,If we don't go now, It won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.50,0:25:00.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,明白嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.50,0:25:00.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.40,0:25:01.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.40,0:25:01.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,So, what do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.10,0:25:39.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把手伸出車外
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.10,0:25:39.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Please keep your hands inside the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.20,0:25:58.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我最喜歡吃薄餅的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.20,0:25:58.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,This is my favorite Pizza place.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.10,0:26:02.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,東尼!  來個大薄餅 多加點水藻
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.10,0:26:02.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Tony! One large, extra plankton.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.10,0:26:06.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們時間無多  他們快來了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.10,0:26:06.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We have so little time. They're going to be here any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.40,0:26:08.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 誰? - 他們不想我和你交談
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.40,0:26:08.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Who are? - They don't want me talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.00,0:26:11.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,那就別交談好了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.00,0:26:11.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Then don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.40,0:26:26.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.40,0:26:26.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.40,0:26:29.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 楚門 - 他們想怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.40,0:26:29.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Truman. - What do they want?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.00,0:26:33.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說  人人都清楚你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.00,0:26:33.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Listen to me. Everybody knows about you. Everybody knows everything you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.60,0:26:36.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,人人都在假裝!明白嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.60,0:26:36.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,They're pretending, Truman. Do you understand? Everybody's pretending.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.70,0:26:38.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 羅蘭 我不明白...  - 不 我不是羅蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.70,0:26:38.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Lauren, I don't know...  -No, my name's not Lauren.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.70,0:26:40.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫施維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.70,0:26:40.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's Sylvia. My name's Sylvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.20,0:26:41.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 施維亞? - 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.20,0:26:41.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Sylvia? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.40,0:26:43.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,羅蘭  你又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.40,0:26:43.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Lauren, sweetheart, Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.50,0:26:45.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  你是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.50,0:26:45.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.20,0:26:46.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 她的爸爸  - 什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.20,0:26:46.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- I'm her father  - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.70,0:26:48.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我沒見過他
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.70,0:26:48.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- I've never even Seen him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.00,0:26:50.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,乖女兒  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.00,0:26:50.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Honey, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.50,0:26:53.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,別信他  我說的話都是真的!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.50,0:26:53.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He's lying. Truman, please, Don't listen to him. Everything I've told you is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.10,0:26:57.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,這是假的  都是為你而設的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.10,0:26:57.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,This, it's fake. It's all for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.20,0:27:00.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我不明白  - 什麼都是虛構的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.20,0:27:00.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- I don't understand.  - The sky and the sea, everything...it's a set.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.20,0:27:03.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,是做戲  人人在看你  別信他
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.20,0:27:03.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a show. Everybody's watching you. Please don't listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.50,0:27:05.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他會騙你 小心 他們在觀看我們
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.50,0:27:05.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He's gonna lie to you. They're watching us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.10,0:27:08.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 究竟什麼事?  - 精神分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.10,0:27:08.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- What's going on?  - Schizophrenia. She has episodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.20,0:27:11.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 求求你 不要!  - 我們已經儘量醫她
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.20,0:27:11.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Please. Oh, no! - We've tried Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.40,0:27:16.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心 你不是第一個
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.40,0:27:16.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You're not the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.70,0:27:19.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不要聽他的  - 她把所有男朋友都帶來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.70,0:27:19.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Don't listen to him. - She brings all her boyfriends down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.40,0:27:21.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他在說什麼? 楚門  他在騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.40,0:27:21.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What's he saying? Truman, he's lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.70,0:27:24.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你要逃出去  逃出去找我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.70,0:27:24.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Get out of here. Come and find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.00,0:27:26.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在學校再見
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.00,0:27:26.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll see you at school
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.10,0:27:28.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要搬去菲濟
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.10,0:27:28.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Fiji. We're moving to Fiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.40,0:27:29.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,菲濟?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.40,0:27:29.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Fiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.60,0:27:43.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,施維亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.60,0:27:43.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Sylvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.80,0:27:55.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他為什麼不跟她去菲濟?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.80,0:27:55.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Why didn't he just follow her to Fiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.70,0:27:58.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他媽媽患了大病
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.70,0:27:58.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,His mother got sick, really sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.80,0:28:01.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他孝順  不忍心離開 也許太孝順了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.80,0:28:01.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He couldn't leave her. He's kind. Maybe he's too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.30,0:28:05.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他失去羅蘭不久  就娶了美露
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.30,0:28:05.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't believe he married Meryl on the rebound.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.50,0:28:06.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.50,0:28:06.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.50,0:28:10.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已有那段劇情的影帶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.50,0:28:10.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on, sal. We've already got this on the greatest hits tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.80,0:28:13.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,可以借給我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.80,0:28:13.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Can I borrow that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.20,0:28:27.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,(怎樣收場?)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.80,0:29:02.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,有幾分相像  但不全像
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.80,0:29:02.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Close, but no cigar.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.80,0:29:32.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,世外桃源又一天
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.80,0:29:32.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And it's another beautiful day in paradise, folks
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.70,0:29:36.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,但大家要記著系上安全帶
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.70,0:29:36.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,But don't forget to buckle up out there in radio land.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.60,0:29:48.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,等候提示 等候提示
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.60,0:29:48.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait for the cue. Wait for the cue.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.60,0:29:54.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,準備出動
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.60,0:29:54.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Stand by, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.70,0:30:01.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他沿史超活道西行  臨記準備
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.70,0:30:01.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He's heading west on stewart.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.80,0:30:03.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,90秒後  他會到達
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.80,0:30:03.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Stand by, all extras. He'll be on you in about 90 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.80,0:30:05.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,記得放小狗出來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.80,0:30:05.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Props, make sure the coffee's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.50,0:30:08.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他轉入蘭嘉士打廣場
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.50,0:30:08.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Ok, he's making his turn onto Lancaster Square.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.80,0:30:16.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,天  他差點撞倒人 哪裡出問題了 更改波頻
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.80,0:30:16.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, my god. He nearly hit her. Something's wrong. Change frequencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.70,0:30:23.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我們忙中有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.70,0:30:23.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Ouch. Sorry about that, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.70,0:30:28.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才無意中播放了員警電臺
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.70,0:30:28.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I guess we picked up a police frequency or something. It sometimes happens, And it can drive you crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.50,0:30:31.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是賈禮金曲時間
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.50,0:30:31.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Ok, it's classical clive back in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.20,0:30:33.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們為你準備了精彩的音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.20,0:30:33.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And we've still got some great music up ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.60,0:30:35.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,但大家記緊 扣好安全帶
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.60,0:30:35.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,But hey, don't forget to buckle up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.90,0:30:39.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,小心駛得萬年車  出色的司機是安全的司機
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.90,0:30:39.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Remember safety. A good driver is a safe driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.10,0:30:40.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,安全的司機又是什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.10,0:30:40.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,A safe driver is what? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.40,0:30:45.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,(驅逐流浪漢 桃源島長老忍無可忍)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.60,0:30:58.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.60,0:30:58.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Morning, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.00,0:32:37.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,這方法好
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.00,0:32:37.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I love that idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.80,0:32:38.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,很不賴 是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.80,0:32:38.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's pretty cool, Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.10,0:32:40.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.10,0:32:40.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.70,0:33:44.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,有何貴幹?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.70,0:33:44.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.00,0:33:47.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我約見了基寶企業
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.00,0:33:47.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. I have an appointment at Gable Enterprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.70,0:33:48.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.70,0:33:48.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.40,0:33:55.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 什麼事? - 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.40,0:33:55.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- What's happening? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.80,0:33:57.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,說  什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.80,0:33:57.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Just tell me what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.00,0:33:59.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,請離開  現在正裝修
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.00,0:33:59.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Got to go, sir. We're remodeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.50,0:34:01.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  他們是什麼人?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.50,0:34:01.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,No, you're not. What are those people doing back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.20,0:34:03.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不關你事...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.20,0:34:03.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.10,0:34:05.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你不說  我去報警
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.10,0:34:05.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,If you don't tell me what's happening, I'll report you!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.60,0:34:07.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你擅闖他人地方!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.60,0:34:07.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.30,0:34:11.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.30,0:34:11.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.00,0:34:40.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,馬龍!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.00,0:34:40.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Marlon!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.60,0:34:42.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門  什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.60,0:34:42.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.70,0:34:43.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我想說句話
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.70,0:34:43.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I gotta talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.70,0:34:45.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在沒有空
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.70,0:34:45.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a bad time, Ok? I'm way behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.50,0:34:47.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,有些不尋常的事  很不尋常
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.50,0:34:47.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm onto something, Marlon. Something big.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.70,0:34:49.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你面色發青
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.70,0:34:49.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You Ok? You look like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.90,0:34:52.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我可能惹上麻煩 - 什麼麻煩?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.90,0:34:52.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- I think I'm mixed up in something. - Mixed up in what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.60,0:34:55.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,很難解釋  總之千奇百怪
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.60,0:34:55.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,There's no point trying to explain it, but a lot of strange things have been happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.90,0:35:04.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,升降機裡面有人  卻沒有牆
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.90,0:35:04.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The people on the elevator. There was no backing on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.80,0:35:06.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我看過去  看到人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.80,0:35:06.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I looked out. There was people there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.60,0:35:08.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我上班途中  聽收音機
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.60,0:35:08.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And on the radio on the way to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.90,0:35:12.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我一舉一動  收音機直接播放
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.90,0:35:12.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It starts following me along, talking about everything that I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.20,0:35:15.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 明白嗎? - 你想像力太豐富了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.20,0:35:15.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- You know what I mean? - Truman, look, this is one of your fantasies.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.10,0:35:17.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 這事跟我爸爸有關 - 你爸爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.10,0:35:17.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- I think this is about my dad. - Your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.60,0:35:18.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能依然活著
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.60,0:35:18.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I think he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.70,0:35:23.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,之後再慢慢跟你說 一定有人在跟蹤我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.70,0:35:23.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll tell you about it later. I'm definitely being followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.10,0:35:25.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,誰在跟蹤你?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.10,0:35:25.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.30,0:35:30.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,很難說  似乎是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.30,0:35:30.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's hard to tell. They look just like regular people.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.20,0:35:35.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩個呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.20,0:35:35.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,How about those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.90,0:35:37.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.90,0:35:37.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know. Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.30,0:35:41.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我一有突發舉動  他們就...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.30,0:35:41.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's when I'm unpredictable, That's they can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.30,0:35:45.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 有沒有事情發生? - 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.30,0:35:45.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Did anything happen? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.30,0:35:48.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我們要離開這裡了 跟我走  行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.30,0:35:48.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Mm-hmm. We gotta get out of here. - You ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.20,0:35:49.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不行 我才剛找到這份工作 - 來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.20,0:35:49.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- No. I just came here. - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.10,0:35:51.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不行就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.10,0:35:51.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I told you I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.90,0:35:57.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都會被炒魷魚
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.90,0:35:57.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're gonna get both our asses fired. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.10,0:36:00.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 無所謂 大膽做 - 什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.10,0:36:00.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Ok, man, Let's do it. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.10,0:36:02.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎樣就怎樣 我的地盤我做主
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.10,0:36:02.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Whatever you say. I'm game
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.80,0:36:03.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.80,0:36:03.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.00,0:36:07.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  生日  一年只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.00,0:36:07.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, siree. Your birthday comes but once a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.20,0:36:13.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能受到別人操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.20,0:36:13.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm being set up for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.10,0:36:15.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你有沒有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.10,0:36:15.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You ever think about that, Marlon?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.90,0:36:18.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,好像一生都身不由己
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.90,0:36:18.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,like your whole life has been building towards something?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.20,0:36:20.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.20,0:36:20.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Mmm, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.80,0:36:25.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,那年夏天  你替凱撒運雞...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.80,0:36:25.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,When you were hauling chickens in the summer for Kaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.30,0:36:27.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,離開過桃源島  到過哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.30,0:36:27.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What was the furthest you ever got off the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.90,0:36:31.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼地方都到過  但都不及這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.90,0:36:31.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Went all over. Never found a place like this, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.00,0:36:34.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,看看這日落
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.00,0:36:34.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Look at that sunset, Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.90,0:36:36.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,瑰麗無比
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.90,0:36:36.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.90,0:36:40.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,對  上帝的傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.90,0:36:40.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's the big guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.70,0:36:43.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直鬼斧神工
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.70,0:36:43.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Quite a paintbrush he's got.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.40,0:36:50.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要告訴別人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.40,0:36:50.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Just between you and me, Marlon...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.20,0:36:54.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算出外走走
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.20,0:36:54.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm going away for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.60,0:36:56.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.60,0:36:56.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.00,0:36:57.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.00,0:36:57.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.10,0:37:01.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,小天使
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.10,0:37:01.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, little angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.90,0:37:09.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,小笑彈
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.90,0:37:09.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, my little clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.00,0:37:13.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,紅蘿蔔頭
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.00,0:37:13.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Old carrot top.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.40,0:37:16.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,最好的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.40,0:37:16.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The best photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.70,0:37:19.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,應該送你回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.70,0:37:19.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We should be getting you home, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.20,0:37:21.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.20,0:37:21.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.30,0:37:23.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在偉人石像前拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.30,0:37:23.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Here's us at Mount Rushmore.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.50,0:37:26.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,記得嗎? 你的爸爸當時還在生
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.50,0:37:26.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you remember, Truman? When dad was still with us
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.10,0:37:29.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,車程很遠  你一直在車裡睡
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.10,0:37:29.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That was quite a drive. You slept the whole way there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.20,0:37:31.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,石像看來很小
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.20,0:37:31.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It looks so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.70,0:37:34.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,回憶裡的東西總比真實的小
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.70,0:37:34.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Things always do when you look back, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.20,0:37:38.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  那是我們最快樂的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.20,0:37:38.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, look, Truman. The happiest day of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.70,0:37:43.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,看  珍 茱迪 鐘安
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.70,0:37:43.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, look. Jean, Jodie, Joanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.80,0:37:45.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,她多漂亮  對不對?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.80,0:37:45.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Doesn't she look beautiful, Truman?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.20,0:37:48.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.20,0:37:48.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, she still does.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.40,0:37:51.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,還有很多空頁可以貼小孩照片
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.40,0:37:51.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And there's lots of pages left over for baby photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.40,0:37:55.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望有生之年能抱孫子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.40,0:37:55.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I would like to hold a grandchild in my arms before I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.90,0:37:57.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我們應該送你回家 - 我送她
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.90,0:37:57.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Angela, we really should be getting you home. - I'll take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.90,0:38:00.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你坐著  休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.90,0:38:00.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,No, no, no. You stay, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.80,0:38:02.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡的節目快播映了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.80,0:38:02.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Enjoy yourself. Your favorite show will be coming on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.90,0:38:05.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,況且  美露和我有些話想說
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.90,0:38:05.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Besides, we have something to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.80,0:38:08.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,關於某人的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.80,0:38:08.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,A certain person's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.30,0:38:10.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.30,0:38:10.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.50,0:38:14.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,明天繼續收看"我愛露絲"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.50,0:38:14.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And there'll be another episode of "I love lucy" same time tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.50,0:38:17.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是"懷舊名片"時間
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.50,0:38:17.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,But right now it's time for golden oldies.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.80,0:38:20.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我們播映膾炙人口的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.80,0:38:20.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Tonight, we present The enduring, much-loved classic
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.40,0:38:22.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,"歸心似箭"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.40,0:38:22.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Show me the way to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.70,0:38:25.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,本片歌頌小鎮生活
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.70,0:38:25.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,A hymn of praise to small-town life,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.20,0:38:27.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,令我們體驗到在家千日好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.20,0:38:27.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Where we learn that you don't have to leave home
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.40,0:38:32.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,故鄉的濃厚人情味
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.40,0:38:32.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,to discover what the world's all about, and that no one is poor who has friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.90,0:38:35.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,悲歡離合  笑中有淚
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.90,0:38:35.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Full of laughter and love, pain and sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.30,0:38:37.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,迷途知返
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.30,0:38:37.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,But ultimately redemption,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.20,0:38:39.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們見證柯家的奮鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.20,0:38:39.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We share the trials and tribulations of the Abbott family.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.00,0:38:43.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,畢朗奴飾演叔叔  感人肺腑
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.00,0:38:43.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Note the touching performance of Ronald Brierly as Uncle Buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.20,0:38:48.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,那碗櫻桃的一幕保證各位捧腹
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.20,0:38:48.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And that scene with the bowl of cherries is gonna have you splitting your sides with laughter all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.40,0:38:52.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,大衛 珍妮花重逢  賺人熱淚
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.40,0:38:52.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And there'll be tears, too, when David and Jennifer are reunited.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.80,0:38:54.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我不再多講
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.80,0:38:54.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,But enough from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.10,0:38:56.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就送上錦丹村的柯家
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.10,0:38:56.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's join the Abbotts in Camden Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.30,0:39:25.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.30,0:39:25.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh. Thank you, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.40,0:39:33.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我到外面去  我有話想說
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.40,0:39:33.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I need to talk to you, But let's go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.50,0:39:36.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想聽  但要趕時間
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.50,0:39:36.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, sweetie, I'd love to, but I'm really late.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.80,0:39:38.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,到哪裡去?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.80,0:39:38.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What's your rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.20,0:39:40.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,做手術
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.20,0:39:40.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.50,0:39:43.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,升降機發生意外  新聞有報導
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.50,0:39:43.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,There was that elevator disaster downtown. It was on the news last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.60,0:39:45.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼纜斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.60,0:39:45.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,This cable just snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.50,0:39:48.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,電梯間從十樓跌下  乘客非死則傷
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.50,0:39:48.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,This elevator, it just plummeted down 10 flights.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.10,0:39:49.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面是臨時工
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.10,0:39:49.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The non-union workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.00,0:39:54.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,那部升降機在你公司附近
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.00,0:39:54.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Just monsters. You know, that building, it's right next door to where you are working.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.20,0:39:55.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好你沒有搭
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.20,0:39:55.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you imagine if you had been in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.80,0:39:57.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,否則不堪設想
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.80,0:39:57.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not even worth thinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.10,0:40:01.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,有位女乘客要做切肢手術
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.10,0:40:01.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Anyway, I have an amputation on one of the young women in that elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.30,0:40:03.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,她很年輕的  真不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.30,0:40:03.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,She's very young. It's very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.00,0:40:05.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,祝我順利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.00,0:40:05.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Anyway, wish me luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.80,0:40:07.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我會疊手指  祝你順利
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.80,0:40:07.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll cross my fingers for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.40,0:40:52.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 請問你什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.40,0:40:52.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh, excuse me. Hi. Excuse me. May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.30,0:40:57.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我太太美露是這裡的護士 我有事要找她
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.30,0:40:57.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, Uh...Yes. I'm looking for my wife, Nurse Burbank.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.70,0:41:02.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 很重要的事  - 恐怕不可以  她要做手術
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.70,0:41:02.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- It's very important. - I'm afraid that's not possible. She's in pre-op.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.60,0:41:07.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,替我傳個口訊  行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.60,0:41:07.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Sure. Ok, fine. Can you pass along a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.40,0:41:08.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我會試試
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.40,0:41:08.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.60,0:41:12.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去菲濟 抵達後會致電給她
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.60,0:41:12.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you tell her I had to go to Fiji and that I'll call her when I get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.30,0:41:14.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,抵達菲濟後?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.30,0:41:14.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,When you... When you get to Fiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.90,0:41:16.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.90,0:41:16.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.20,0:41:18.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我會告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.20,0:41:18.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.60,0:41:20.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感激
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.60,0:41:20.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.40,0:41:48.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 對不起 - 不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.40,0:41:48.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Sorry. - It's Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.40,0:41:51.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.40,0:41:51.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Let me help you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.10,0:41:57.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.10,0:41:57.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.60,0:42:01.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.60,0:42:01.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I know, Shh, shh, shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.10,0:42:03.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,解剖刀
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.10,0:42:03.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Scalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.10,0:42:14.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在在右膝上...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.10,0:42:14.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm now making my primary incision...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.30,0:42:17.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,做初步切割
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.30,0:42:17.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Just above the right knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.90,0:42:21.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,按著她
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.90,0:42:21.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hold her
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.50,0:42:23.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,割得恰到好處
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.50,0:42:23.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Nicely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.10,0:42:27.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼好看  除非你是家屬
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.10,0:42:27.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,This isn't going to be pretty, Unless you are family.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.60,0:42:29.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你手術的確高明
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.60,0:42:29.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's just beautiful. Beautiful job.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.60,0:42:33.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,讓其他人來收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.60,0:42:33.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll just let someone else tidy up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.40,0:43:01.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 要你等  對不起 - 不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.40,0:43:01.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry to keep you. - Oh, that's Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.50,0:43:04.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,可以效勞嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.50,0:43:04.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.50,0:43:07.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,一張去菲濟的機票
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.50,0:43:07.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I would like to book a flight to Fiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.20,0:43:11.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,幾時出發?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.20,0:43:11.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,When would you like to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.60,0:43:13.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,今天
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.60,0:43:13.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.10,0:43:34.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  起碼要一個月後才有位
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.10,0:43:34.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I don't have anything for at least a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.80,0:43:36.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,一個月後?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.80,0:43:36.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,A month?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.20,0:43:38.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是旺季
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.20,0:43:38.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's the busy season.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.30,0:43:41.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要訂位?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.30,0:43:41.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You want to book the flight?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.40,0:43:46.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不要了  我試試其他交通工具
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.40,0:43:46.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter. I'll make other arrangements, Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.30,0:43:53.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,往芝加哥乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.30,0:43:53.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Last call for Chicago
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.50,0:43:55.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,所有乘客上車
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.50,0:43:55.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,All aboard
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.70,0:44:01.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.70,0:44:01.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.50,0:44:07.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,風中之城芝加哥  我們來也
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.50,0:44:07.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Windy city, here we come.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.20,0:44:10.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.20,0:44:10.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.70,0:44:14.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.70,0:44:14.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.50,0:44:17.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.50,0:44:17.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.80,0:44:18.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,修女
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.80,0:44:18.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.80,0:44:21.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽  那個人是不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.80,0:44:21.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, mom, isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.30,0:44:23.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,看前面  乖女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.30,0:44:23.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Shh. Face the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.80,0:44:52.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,各位下車  機件故障
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.80,0:44:52.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Everybody off. We've got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.20,0:45:13.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  小夥子
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.20,0:45:13.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.50,0:45:28.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他的爸爸是芝加哥人  對嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.50,0:45:28.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,His father was from Chicago, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.90,0:45:32.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不  他的牙醫是佛羅里達人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.90,0:45:32.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,No. His dentist was from Pensacola.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.40,0:45:33.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他爸爸是愛荷華人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.40,0:45:33.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,His father was from Desmoines.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.80,0:45:36.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼去芝加哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.80,0:45:36.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,But how come he wants to go to Chicago?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.20,0:45:38.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他不想去  哪裡也不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.20,0:45:38.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He's not going to Chicago. He's not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.90,0:45:40.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,只是和美露鬥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.90,0:45:40.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He has to have it out with Meryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.20,0:45:58.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.20,0:45:58.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.50,0:46:04.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.50,0:46:04.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Honey, are you Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.20,0:46:07.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,上車
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.20,0:46:07.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.40,0:46:11.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.40,0:46:11.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.20,0:46:14.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.20,0:46:14.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.40,0:46:18.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.40,0:46:18.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What? Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.30,0:46:22.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,待會兒將會見到...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.30,0:46:22.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I predict that in just a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.30,0:46:26.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,一位太太騎著紅色單車
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.30,0:46:26.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We will see a lady on a red bike,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.80,0:46:28.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,然後有個人拿著鮮花
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.80,0:46:28.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Followed by a man with flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.70,0:46:32.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,跟著有架黃色甲蟲型福士
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.70,0:46:32.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And a volkswagen beetle with a dented fender.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.80,0:46:35.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 楚門  拜託. - 看
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.80,0:46:35.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Truman, please. - look.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.90,0:46:42.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,太太...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.90,0:46:42.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.40,0:46:44.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,鮮花...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.40,0:46:44.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.50,0:46:48.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.50,0:46:48.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.60,0:46:51.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,太無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.60,0:46:51.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman, this is silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.90,0:46:53.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.90,0:46:53.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,There it is! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.70,0:46:55.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,一架黃色福士!是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.70,0:46:55.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,There's that dented beetle! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.20,0:47:04.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我怎猜中嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.20,0:47:04.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't you want to know how I did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.70,0:47:07.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,很簡單  他們在兜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.70,0:47:07.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll tell you. They're on a loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.50,0:47:10.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,沿著附近幾條街  不斷兜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.50,0:47:10.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,They go around the block. They come back. They go around again.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.70,0:47:13.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他們就那樣團團轉
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.70,0:47:13.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,They just go round and round. Round and round.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.70,0:47:16.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我請了馬龍夫婦周日來燒烤
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.70,0:47:16.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I invited Rita and Marlon for a barbecue on sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.80,0:47:18.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.80,0:47:18.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I won't be here Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.40,0:47:20.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,記得提醒我買炭
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.40,0:47:20.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And I need you to remind me that we need more charcoal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.80,0:47:23.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我的話你有沒有聽見?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.80,0:47:23.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you listening to a word I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.80,0:47:28.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你講來講去  都要去菲濟
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.80,0:47:28.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're upset because you want to go to Fiji. Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.60,0:47:33.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.60,0:47:33.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Ok, Ok, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.50,0:47:39.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,但應該儲幾個月的生活費才去
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.50,0:47:39.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I think you should save for a few months and then go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.00,0:47:42.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,現在滿意了沒有?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.00,0:47:42.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.30,0:47:45.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我去洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.30,0:47:45.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to go take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.90,0:47:47.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.90,0:47:47.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.80,0:47:50.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在可以去了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.80,0:47:50.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm ready to go now. Why wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.00,0:47:53.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,坐言起行  早走早著  對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.00,0:47:53.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Early bird gathers no moss. Rolling stone catches the worm, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.80,0:47:58.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.80,0:47:58.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman, What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.30,0:48:03.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.30,0:48:03.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.30,0:48:07.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,應該駛到哪裡去?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.30,0:48:07.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Where shall we go? Where shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.00,0:48:10.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門  我們去哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.00,0:48:10.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.40,0:48:12.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是漫無目的  順其自然
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.40,0:48:12.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't really know. I guess I'm being spontaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.90,0:48:17.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了  我順其自然起來!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.90,0:48:17.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Somebody help me! I'm being spontaneous!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.50,0:48:21.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不去菲濟了  反正開車去不到
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.50,0:48:21.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman. forget Fiji. Can't very well drive to Fiji, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.90,0:48:27.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不如去大西洋城?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.90,0:48:27.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What about Atlantic City?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.40,0:48:29.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不要去  你討厭賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.40,0:48:29.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, no, you hate to gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.60,0:48:32.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 的確討厭  - 為什麼還去?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.60,0:48:32.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- That's right, I do, don't I?  - So why would you want to go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.50,0:48:33.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,因為沒去過
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.50,0:48:33.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Because I never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.00,0:48:36.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,觀光就是去沒去過的地方,不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.00,0:48:36.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why people go places, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.00,0:48:40.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門  我想嘔吐
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.00,0:48:40.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman, Truman, I think I'm gonna throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.40,0:48:41.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.40,0:48:41.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.70,0:48:52.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,到處都塞車
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.70,0:48:52.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Blocked at every turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.10,0:48:54.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,配合得天衣無縫  對嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.10,0:48:54.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Beautifully synchronized, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.90,0:48:56.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,連塞車你也怪我?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.90,0:48:56.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're blaming me for the traffic?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.00,0:48:58.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不應該怪你?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.00,0:48:58.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.80,0:49:08.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.80,0:49:08.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman...Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.10,0:49:12.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,好  塞車可能塞幾個鐘頭
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.10,0:49:12.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're right. We could be stuck here for hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.00,0:49:15.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,一直塞到大西洋城  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.00,0:49:15.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It could be like this all the way to Atlantic City. Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.00,0:49:20.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我一時糊塗  不應該去
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.00,0:49:20.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I don't know what got into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.30,0:49:26.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,可以駛慢一點嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.30,0:49:26.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you please slow down?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.30,0:49:28.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.30,0:49:28.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.20,0:49:33.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你忘記轉彎! - 我又改變主意
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.20,0:49:33.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Truman! Truman! That's our turnoff! - I changed my mind again.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.60,0:49:35.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,新奧爾良這幾天應該好熱鬧不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.60,0:49:35.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What's new orleans like this time of year?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.60,0:49:37.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,是狂歡節!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.60,0:49:37.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Mardi gras! Whoo! Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.80,0:49:47.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,看  同一條路  一部車都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.80,0:49:47.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Look, Meryl, same road, No cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.90,0:49:48.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,像魔術一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.90,0:49:48.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's magic. Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.70,0:49:52.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我要下車  你的腦袋有毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.70,0:49:52.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You let me out. You're not right in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.90,0:49:54.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你要自毀  自毀到夠
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.90,0:49:54.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You want to destroy yourself, do it on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.20,0:49:56.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我要人陪
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.20,0:49:56.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I think I'd like a little company.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.00,0:50:08.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你明知故犯
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.00,0:50:08.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, Truman... You knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.40,0:50:11.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,明知道自己不敢開車過海
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.40,0:50:11.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You know you can't drive over water.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.60,0:50:14.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,回家吧  你會覺得安全
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.60,0:50:14.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go home where you'll feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.40,0:50:20.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 伸手過來 - 楚門
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.40,0:50:20.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Give me your hand. Sweetie - Truman
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.40,0:50:21.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你轉彎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.40,0:50:21.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.60,0:50:23.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.60,0:50:23.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.50,0:50:26.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以! 這樣做是犯法!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.50,0:50:26.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We shouldn't be doing this! We're breaking the law!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.40,0:50:28.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 天! - 你做得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.40,0:50:28.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Oh, my! - You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.80,0:50:29.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.80,0:50:29.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Please, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.30,0:50:32.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你辦得到! - 楚門!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.30,0:50:32.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- You can make it! - Truman!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.80,0:50:35.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,過了橋!  我們過了橋!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.80,0:50:35.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Aah! Oh, we're over! We're over the bridge! We're over the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.90,0:50:38.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 過了嗎? - 我們過了橋 我們過了橋
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.90,0:50:38.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- We're over?  - We're over the bridge. We're over the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.90,0:50:41.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們過了橋!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.90,0:50:41.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We're over!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.50,0:50:46.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,(山火警告：極度危險)
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.00,0:50:51.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 有山火 怎麼辦? - 誇大其詞  別怕
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.00,0:50:51.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Truman! What about that sign? - They're exaggerating. We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.10,0:50:54.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,誇大其詞? 你相信嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.10,0:50:54.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Exaggerating? Do you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.50,0:51:00.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,著火了!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.50,0:51:00.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, my! Oh, my! Truman, we're on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.30,0:51:03.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,只是煙霧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.30,0:51:03.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's Ok. It's just smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.70,0:51:04.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你沒事吧? - 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.70,0:51:04.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- You Ok? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.00,0:51:06.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 想再試嗎? - 不想!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.00,0:51:06.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Want to do it again? - No! Ha ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.70,0:51:10.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門  停車!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.70,0:51:10.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman, stop! Oh, god!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.90,0:51:16.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒有錢!  到新奧爾良怎辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.90,0:51:16.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh! So, what are we going to do for money when we get to New Orleans?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.10,0:51:20.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我有桃源的銀行卡
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.10,0:51:20.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I have my Seahaven Bank card.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.50,0:51:24.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算吃老本?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.50,0:51:24.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We're just going to eat into our savings, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.60,0:51:27.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,一到達  我要打電話給你媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.60,0:51:27.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm going to have to call your mother when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.50,0:51:28.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,她一定擔心得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.50,0:51:28.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,She's going to be worried sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.60,0:51:31.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,可能受不起打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.60,0:51:31.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know how she's going to take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.80,0:51:45.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,又有什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.80,0:51:45.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.80,0:51:47.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,(牌匾:桃源核電站)紅色警報! 紅色警報!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.80,0:51:47.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Red alert! This is a red alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.00,0:51:54.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,核電站似乎漏輻射
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.00,0:51:54.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman, it looks like a leak at the plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.70,0:51:57.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,掉頭! 核電站漏輻射  要關閉
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.70,0:51:57.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Back up! Back up! Leak at the plant. We had to shut her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.90,0:51:59.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,可不可以繞路?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.90,0:51:59.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Is there any way around?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.10,0:52:00.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,全區都要疏散
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.10,0:52:00.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Whole area's being evacuated.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.70,0:52:02.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 要我幫忙嗎? - 不用
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.70,0:52:02.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Is there anything I can do?  - No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.40,0:52:04.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 謝謝你 - 不用客氣  楚門
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.40,0:52:04.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Thank you for your help. - You're welcome, Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.20,0:52:08.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.20,0:52:08.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.00,0:52:12.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門! 楚門!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.00,0:52:12.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman! Truman!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.60,0:52:14.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門...回來!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.60,0:52:14.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman...come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.80,0:52:18.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,截停他!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.80,0:52:18.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman! Truman! Stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.00,0:52:21.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.00,0:52:21.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Unh! Truman!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.90,0:52:25.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他往出口竄去!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.90,0:52:25.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Head to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.40,0:52:41.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不要走過來!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.40,0:52:41.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.00,0:52:50.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.00,0:52:50.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Unh! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.20,0:52:52.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.20,0:52:52.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.00,0:52:54.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,已經控制好狀況了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.00,0:52:54.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Now in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.60,0:53:00.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩了你們  很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.60,0:53:00.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you both so much for your help. I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.10,0:53:04.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,這次放過他  下次我們要檢控
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.10,0:53:04.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He's lucky to be alive, ma'am. Next time, we'll have to file charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.50,0:53:05.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.50,0:53:05.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.70,0:53:08.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 再次謝謝你們  晚安  - 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.70,0:53:08.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Thanks again. Good night. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.70,0:53:29.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要接受治療
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.70,0:53:29.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Let me get you some help, Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.10,0:53:31.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你有病
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.10,0:53:31.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're not well.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.10,0:53:36.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要替我生孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.10,0:53:36.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Why do you want to have a baby with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.70,0:53:39.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.70,0:53:39.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You can't stand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.80,0:53:41.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.80,0:53:41.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.20,0:53:48.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我去倒杯莫可哥給你?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.20,0:53:48.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Why don't you let me fix you some of this new mococoa drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.80,0:53:52.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,尼加拉瓜山天然可哥煉製
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.80,0:53:52.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,All natural cocoa beans from the upper slopes of Mount Nicaragua.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.20,0:53:53.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不含人工糖分
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.20,0:53:53.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,No artificial sweeteners.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.00,0:53:55.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.00,0:53:55.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.70,0:53:58.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,跟誰說話?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.70,0:53:58.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Who are you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.00,0:54:02.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,各種可哥中  莫可哥最好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.00,0:54:02.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I've tasted other cocoas. This is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.60,0:54:06.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我們有什麼關係?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.60,0:54:06.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What the hell does this have to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.90,0:54:08.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟什麼事!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.90,0:54:08.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Tell me what's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.00,0:54:12.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你還問? 你自己精神崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.00,0:54:12.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're having a nervous breakdown, that's what happing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.20,0:54:14.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你有份  對不對?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.20,0:54:14.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're part of this, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.10,0:54:19.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 楚門! - 美露!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.10,0:54:19.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Truman! - Meryl!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.60,0:54:22.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你嚇怕了我!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.60,0:54:22.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You...are...scaring me!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.20,0:54:24.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你才嚇怕了我
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.20,0:54:24.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,No, you're scaring me, Meryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.20,0:54:26.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎樣處置我?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.20,0:54:26.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.70,0:54:29.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,剁? 切? 削?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.70,0:54:29.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Dice me? Slice me or peel me?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.60,0:54:31.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,多種選擇!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.60,0:54:31.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,There are so many choices!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.90,0:54:33.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,快想想辦法!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.90,0:54:33.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Aah! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.60,0:54:38.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.60,0:54:38.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.10,0:54:40.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟誰說話?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.10,0:54:40.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Who are you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.20,0:54:43.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有說話  什麼也沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.20,0:54:43.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Nothing. I didn't say anything. I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.20,0:54:46.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你有說 - 我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.20,0:54:46.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- You said, "do something." - No, I didn't. I wasn't talking to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.20,0:54:50.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 告訴我! - 我毫不知情!  停手!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.20,0:54:50.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Talk to me! - I don't know anything! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.10,0:54:52.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不要動!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.10,0:54:52.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.70,0:54:54.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.70,0:54:54.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.00,0:54:58.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門?\N楚門?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.00,0:54:58.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.70,0:55:00.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,謝天謝地!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.70,0:55:00.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, thank god! Oh, thank god!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.70,0:55:10.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我怎忍受下去?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.70,0:55:10.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,How can anyone expect me to carry on under these conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.60,0:55:13.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有專業精神!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.60,0:55:13.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's unprofessional!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.80,0:55:15.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不要怕
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.80,0:55:15.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Shh, it's Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.70,0:55:20.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  不要怕
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.70,0:55:20.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Everything's gonna be Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.20,0:55:21.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.20,0:55:21.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, god!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.40,0:55:23.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都會好的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.40,0:55:23.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's all gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.80,0:55:27.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我腦袋一片混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.80,0:55:27.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know what to think, Marlon.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.10,0:55:34.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,快要瘋了 但...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.10,0:55:34.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm losing my mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.10,0:55:41.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,全世界似乎繞著我而轉
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.10,0:55:41.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It feels like the whole world revolves around me somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.30,0:55:47.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,即是說  你自以為好重要
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.30,0:55:47.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That's a lot of world for one man, Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.10,0:55:51.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不是有點一廂情願嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.10,0:55:51.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Sure that's not wishful thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.80,0:55:54.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你感覺鬱鬱不得志?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.80,0:55:54.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You wishing you'd made something more out of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.10,0:55:57.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不得志是很正常的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.10,0:55:57.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on, who hasn't sat in the john,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.60,0:56:00.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也希望躊躇滿志
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.60,0:56:00.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Had an imaginary interview on Seahaven tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.80,0:56:02.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也希望做個名人
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.80,0:56:02.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Who hasn't wanted to be somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.70,0:56:05.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是人人都似乎在串謀
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.70,0:56:05.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,This is different. Everybody seems to be in on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.30,0:56:13.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你七歲時  我們已經是老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.30,0:56:13.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I've been your best friend since we were 7 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.00,0:56:18.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,讀書考試  你抄我  我抄你
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.00,0:56:18.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The only way you and I ever made it through school was by cheating off each other's test papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.30,0:56:21.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你我的答案一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.30,0:56:21.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Jesus, they were identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.80,0:56:25.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我總覺得安全
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.80,0:56:25.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,But I always felt safe knowing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.90,0:56:28.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,因為無論答對還是答錯
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.90,0:56:28.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,'Cause whatever the answer was,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.90,0:56:31.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都能夠一同對  一同錯
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.90,0:56:31.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We were right together and we were wrong together.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.00,0:56:36.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,那一晚去露營  通宵不睡
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.00,0:56:36.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Remember when I stayed up all night in your tent
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.90,0:56:38.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你要扮北極
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.90,0:56:38.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,'Cause you wanted to play north pole?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.90,0:56:41.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,搞到我得肺炎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.90,0:56:41.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And I got pneumonia?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.30,0:56:44.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,記得嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.30,0:56:44.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.40,0:56:48.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你要向學校請了一個月的病假
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.40,0:56:48.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You were out of school for about a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.20,0:56:56.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你我親如兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.20,0:56:56.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're the closest thing I ever had to a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.80,0:57:05.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.80,0:57:05.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I know that things...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.70,0:57:08.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你我的人生都不算順利
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.70,0:57:08.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Haven't really worked out for either of us
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.50,0:57:10.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,離理想相當遠
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.50,0:57:10.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,like we used to dream they would.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.90,0:57:14.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得時不與我...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.90,0:57:14.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I know that feeling, When it's like everything's slipping away...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.80,0:57:18.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你無法面對現實  於是...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.80,0:57:18.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't want to believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.40,0:57:21.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,疑神疑鬼...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.40,0:57:21.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,So you look for answers somewhere else, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.10,0:57:33.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,但我肯為你這朋友  兩脅插刀
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.10,0:57:33.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Well...the point is...I'd gladly walk in front of traffic for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.80,0:57:42.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,但我肯為你這朋友  兩脅插刀
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.80,0:57:42.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Well...The point is, I would gladly step in front of traffic for you, Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.90,0:57:48.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,怎也不會欺騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.90,0:57:48.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And the last thing I'd ever do is lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.20,0:57:52.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,怎也不會...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.20,0:57:52.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And the last thing That I would ever do...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.80,0:57:57.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,欺騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.80,0:57:57.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Is lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.20,0:58:02.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你不妨想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.20,0:58:02.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, think about it, Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.00,0:58:04.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,假如人人都串謀...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.00,0:58:04.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,If everybody is in on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.90,0:58:09.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,即是說  我也串謀
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.90,0:58:09.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'd have to be in on it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.30,0:58:20.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有串謀  因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.30,0:58:20.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not in on it, Truman, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.80,0:58:23.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,根本沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.80,0:58:23.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,There is no "it."
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.20,0:58:29.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一件事你是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.20,0:58:29.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You were right about one thing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.90,0:58:31.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.90,0:58:31.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.50,0:58:35.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,這場風波的起因
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.50,0:58:35.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The thing that started all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.00,0:58:53.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我替你找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.00,0:58:53.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yep. I found him for you, Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.30,0:58:56.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我今晚來找你
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.30,0:58:56.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why I came by tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.80,0:58:59.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他必定有很多話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.80,0:58:59.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's got quite a story to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.10,0:59:04.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.10,0:59:04.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Go to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.40,0:59:12.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,煙霧不要太濃
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.40,0:59:12.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Easy on the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.00,0:59:16.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,吊臂攝影機準備
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.00,0:59:16.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Stand by, crane cam.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.00,0:59:19.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,吊臂攝影機
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.00,0:59:19.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Crane cam.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.00,0:59:28.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,按攝影機三號
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.00,0:59:28.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Button cam 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.20,0:59:43.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都相信你沒遇難
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.20,0:59:43.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I never stopped believing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.60,0:59:49.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,用廣角鏡  路邊攝影機八號
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.60,0:59:49.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And wide, curb cam 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.20,0:59:51.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,乖兒子!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.20,0:59:51.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,My son! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.60,0:59:55.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 要不要特寫? - 暫時不要
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.60,0:59:55.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Move in for a closeup? - No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.40,0:59:58.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.40,0:59:58.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Move back and
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.40,1:00:00.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,加強配樂
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.40,1:00:00.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Fade up music.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.60,1:00:08.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,現在特寫
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.60,1:00:08.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And now go in close.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.00,1:00:12.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼多年  白白過去
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.00,1:00:12.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,All those years wasted.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.90,1:00:15.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我會彌補你的損失
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.90,1:00:15.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll make it up to you, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.00,1:00:17.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.00,1:00:17.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I swear.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.40,1:00:24.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.40,1:00:24.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.10,1:00:27.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.10,1:00:27.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.50,1:00:38.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,很精彩
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.50,1:00:38.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Bravo.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.40,1:00:42.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好艱辛的歷程 - 恭喜
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.40,1:00:42.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- That was a really great experience. - Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.10,1:00:44.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,大家靜一點  留神
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.10,1:00:44.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Ok, quiet down. Let's concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.60,1:00:46.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.60,1:00:46.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That was good work.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.50,1:00:49.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,開香檳慶祝
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.50,1:00:49.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's get some champagne up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.00,1:00:54.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,克裡斯多夫  太精彩了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.00,1:00:54.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Brilliant, Christof. Just brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.00,1:00:55.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼感人肺腑
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.00,1:00:55.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It just broke my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.60,1:01:02.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,大家幹得好!  恭喜
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.60,1:01:02.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Well done, everyone! Congratulations
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.60,1:01:14.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,(楚門喝尼加拉瓜山出產)
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.30,1:01:17.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,(由頂級可哥煉製的莫可哥)
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.20,1:01:23.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,十七億人見證他出生
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.20,1:01:23.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,1.7 billion were there for his birth.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.60,1:01:26.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,(巨星誕生)
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.40,1:01:30.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,220個國家收看他學走路
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.40,1:01:30.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,220 countries tuned in for his first step.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.30,1:01:35.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,舉世靜觀他初吻
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.30,1:01:35.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The world stood still for that stolen kiss,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.20,1:01:37.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他與科技並肩成長
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.20,1:01:37.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And as he grew, so did the technology.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.00,1:01:42.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人的一生 由秘密攝影網路記錄下來
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.00,1:01:42.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,An entire human life recorded on an intricate network of hidden cameras
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.50,1:01:46.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,原汁原味  一天二十四小時
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.50,1:01:46.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And broadcast live and unedited 24 hours a day,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.30,1:01:49.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,在全球不停直播
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.30,1:01:49.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,7 days a week to an audience around the globe.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.50,1:01:56.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,桃源島是一個 規模空前龐大的片場
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.50,1:01:56.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Coming to you now from Seahaven Island, enclosed in the largest studio ever constructed
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.60,1:01:59.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,從太空俯瞰地球可以看到的建築
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.60,1:01:59.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And along with the Great Wall of China,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.10,1:02:02.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有桃源島和萬里長城
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.10,1:02:02.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,One of only two manmade structures visible from space,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.30,1:02:07.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,光輝的第三十年  正是真人秀
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.30,1:02:07.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Now in its 30th great year, It's the Truman show
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.00,1:02:14.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,過去一個星期
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.00,1:02:14.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What a week it's been.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.40,1:02:17.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮迭起  好戲連場
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.40,1:02:17.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know about you...I was on pins and needles the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.30,1:02:20.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,各位觀眾好  我是米高
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.30,1:02:20.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello and good evening. I'm your host Mike Michaelson,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.30,1:02:24.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎收看"真人表演"的 清談節目"真話"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.30,1:02:24.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And welcome to tru-talk, our forum for issues growing out of the show.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.20,1:02:27.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚千載難逢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.20,1:02:27.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,But tonight, something very special indeed,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.20,1:02:31.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,會獨家專訪 "真人表演"的創作人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.20,1:02:31.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,A rare and exclusive interview with the show's conceiver and creator.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.70,1:02:39.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們上去天網攝製 221樓的太陰室
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.70,1:02:39.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,So, come with us now as we go live to the lunar room on the 221st floor of the Omni Cam Echosphere
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.10,1:02:42.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,採訪超級電視攝製的先驅
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.10,1:02:42.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Where we'll find the world's greatest tele-visionary
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.60,1:02:46.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,桃源島的設計者和總監
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.60,1:02:46.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The designer and architect of the world within a world
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.70,1:02:48.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,克裡斯多夫
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.70,1:02:48.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That is Seahaven Island... Christof.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.30,1:02:53.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我先代表觀眾多謝你接受專訪
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.30,1:02:53.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Before we begin, I'd like to thank you on behalf of our audience for granting this interview.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.80,1:02:59.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們知道你工作繁忙 一向作風都是儘量低調
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.80,1:02:59.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We know how demanding your schedule is and we all know how jealously you guard your privacy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.30,1:03:01.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠採訪你  我深感榮幸
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.30,1:03:01.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,This, sir, is indeed an honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.70,1:03:02.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不要客氣
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.70,1:03:02.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.80,1:03:06.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,"真人表演"最近的一波三折
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.80,1:03:06.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, the catalyst for the recent dramatic events
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.40,1:03:09.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,起因是楚門的父親偷偷回去
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.40,1:03:09.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,On the show has been Truman's father, Kirk
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.10,1:03:11.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,外面的人擅闖桃源要接觸楚門
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.10,1:03:11.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And his attempts to infiltrate the show.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.40,1:03:13.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,但切入這話題之前 我認為也沒什麼大不了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.40,1:03:13.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,But before we get into that, I think it's worth noting
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.50,1:03:16.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,這並不是首次有外人干擾節目
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.50,1:03:16.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That this is not the first time someone from the outside
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.40,1:03:20.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 想要接觸楚門 對不對? - 但都有驚無險
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.40,1:03:20.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Has attempted to reach Truman, is it? - We have had close calls in the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.20,1:03:22.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門!上電視了!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.20,1:03:22.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman! It's television!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.70,1:03:27.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於上了"真人表演"!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.70,1:03:27.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes! I did it! I'm on the Truman show!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.10,1:03:29.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,但歷來的擅闖事件中
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.10,1:03:29.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,But there's never been anything to compare
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.70,1:03:32.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,最近這次最嚴重...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.70,1:03:32.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,with this most recent breach in security...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.40,1:03:35.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,因為擅闖的人是前任演員
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.40,1:03:35.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The first intruder to be a former cast member.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.80,1:03:36.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,而且本來已經死了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.80,1:03:36.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,A dead one at that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.10,1:03:41.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你讓卻克復出...  是神來之筆
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.10,1:03:41.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Gotta say, writing Kirk back in...masterstroke.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.10,1:03:43.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這場風波由卻克引起
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.10,1:03:43.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Since Kirk started this crisis in Truman's life,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.60,1:03:46.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為解鈴還須系鈴人
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.60,1:03:46.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I came to the conclusion that only he could end it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.10,1:03:48.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.10,1:03:48.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman! Truman!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.10,1:03:53.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不准過去! - 那裡有什麼?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.10,1:03:53.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- No! That's off limits! - Why? What's over there?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.50,1:03:55.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼  只是危險
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.50,1:03:55.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Nothing. It's dangerous. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.80,1:03:58.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你要記著  有些地方不可以去
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.80,1:03:58.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You've got to know your limitations, Truman.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.40,1:04:02.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,當年為什麼刪除卻克這角色?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.40,1:04:02.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,But let's remind viewers exactly why Dad was written out in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.20,1:04:07.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門長大 我們設法把他留在桃源島
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.20,1:04:07.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,As Truman grew up, we were forced to manufacture ways to keep him on the island.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.90,1:04:10.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我想做探險家  像麥哲倫一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.90,1:04:10.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'd like to be an explorer, like the great Magellan.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.80,1:04:14.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,現在世上已沒什麼好探險的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.80,1:04:14.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're too late. There's really nothing left to explore.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.20,1:04:21.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,於是  我安排卻克浸死
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.20,1:04:21.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Finally, I came up with Kirk's drowning.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.80,1:04:25.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,那辦法很有效  楚門從此怕水
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.80,1:04:25.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Most effective. Truman's been terrified of the water ever since.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.50,1:04:28.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,卻克被迫浸死  退出節目
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.50,1:04:28.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,When Kirk read the synopsis of the episode,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.30,1:04:31.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不消說  失望得很
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.30,1:04:31.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He was disappointed to say the least.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.80,1:04:35.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,於是千方百計潛回片場
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.80,1:04:35.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's what caused him to break onto the set.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.50,1:04:39.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,但你怎解釋他失蹤了二十二年?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.50,1:04:39.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,But how do you intend to explain his 22-year absence?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.30,1:04:41.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,失憶
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.30,1:04:41.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.40,1:04:43.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,高明
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.40,1:04:43.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.50,1:04:44.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,現在接聽觀眾電話
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.50,1:04:44.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's take some viewer phone calls.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.20,1:04:48.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,北卡州的卡露蓮  請說
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.20,1:04:48.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Charlotte, North Carolina, You're on with Christof.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.90,1:04:50.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  克裡斯多夫
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.90,1:04:50.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah, Hi, Christof.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.70,1:04:54.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你在鎮上佈置了多少部攝影機
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.70,1:04:54.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I was wondering how many cameras you got in that town.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.20,1:04:57.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,五千部左右
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.20,1:04:57.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Somewhere in The vicinity of 5,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.50,1:04:59.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,好多
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.50,1:04:59.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That's A lot of cameras.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.10,1:05:02.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,記著  我開始時只用一部
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.10,1:05:02.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Remember, we started with just one.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.90,1:05:08.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他一出生就好奇  早產兩星期
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.90,1:05:08.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He was curious from birth. Premature by 2 weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.70,1:05:10.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,就像迫不及待
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.70,1:05:10.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Almost as if he couldn't wait to get started.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.00,1:05:13.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為他急於走出娘胎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.00,1:05:13.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,His eagerness to leave his mother's womb
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.70,1:05:15.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才獲選
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.70,1:05:15.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Was the very reason he was the one selected
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.90,1:05:18.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們從六個待領養胎兒中
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.90,1:05:18.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,in competition with 5 other unwanted pregnancies,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.70,1:05:21.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,選出楚門  因為楚門...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.70,1:05:21.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The casting of a show, determined by an air date
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.30,1:05:23.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,在現場直播中  準時出世
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.30,1:05:23.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman was the one who arrived on cue.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.60,1:05:31.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門似乎是首名被機構
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.60,1:05:31.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Incidentally, I believe Truman is the first child
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.50,1:05:33.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,合法領養的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.50,1:05:33.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,to have been legally adopted by a corporation.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.20,1:05:34.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.20,1:05:34.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.20,1:05:38.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,節目帶來龐大的收益
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.20,1:05:38.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The show has generated enormous revenues now,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.40,1:05:41.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,相當於一個小國的年產總值
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.40,1:05:41.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Equivalent to the gross national product of a small country.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.50,1:05:44.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,但製作上也需要一國的人手
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.50,1:05:44.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,People forget it takes the population of an entire country to keep the show running.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.90,1:05:48.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,因為二十四小時播放 沒廣告時間
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.90,1:05:48.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Since the show is on 24-hours a day without commercial interruption,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.80,1:05:52.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,收入全靠商品的選用
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.80,1:05:52.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,All those staggering revenues are generated by product placement.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.20,1:05:54.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,對  節目上一切都是發售的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.20,1:05:54.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That's true. Everything on the show is for sale.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.30,1:05:58.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,演員的服裝 食品 住屋等等
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.30,1:05:58.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,From the actor's wardrobe, food products, to the very homes they live in.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.30,1:06:00.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,詳情請參閱真人目錄
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.30,1:06:00.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And all of it available in the Truman catalog.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.00,1:06:02.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎隨時來電查詢
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.00,1:06:02.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Operators are standing by.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.60,1:06:04.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,克裡斯多夫  請問...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.60,1:06:04.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Christof, let me ask you...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.60,1:06:08.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼至今楚門還不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.60,1:06:08.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Why do you think Truman has never come close
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.30,1:06:11.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,自己活在一個什麼樣的世界?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.30,1:06:11.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,to discovering the true nature of his world until now?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.40,1:06:15.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都接受現實
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.40,1:06:15.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We accept the reality of the world with which we are presented.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.40,1:06:16.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.40,1:06:16.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's as simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.40,1:06:22.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,海牙有觀眾打電話來  海牙?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.40,1:06:22.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The Hague for Christof. Hello? The Hague?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.90,1:06:26.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,現在改接好萊塢的電話
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.90,1:06:26.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, We've lost that call. Let's go to Hollywood. You're on tru-talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.90,1:06:31.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,克裡斯多夫  我只想說你好陰險
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.90,1:06:31.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi, Christof. I'd just like to say one thing. You're a liar And a manipulator,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.50,1:06:33.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你的所作所為令人噁心
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.50,1:06:33.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And what you've done to Truman is sick!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.70,1:06:39.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都認得這把聲音 怎能忘記?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.70,1:06:39.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, we remember this voice, don't we? How could we forget?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.60,1:06:41.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不如改接另一個電話
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.60,1:06:41.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go to another call.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.00,1:06:44.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊  米高
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.00,1:06:44.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,No, no, no. It's fine, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.30,1:06:47.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟前度演員聚聚舊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.30,1:06:47.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I love to reminisce with former members of the cast.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.70,1:06:50.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,施維亞...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.70,1:06:50.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Sylvia...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.90,1:06:53.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你當眾沷婦駡街  其實沒意思
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.90,1:06:53.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,As you announced so melodramatically to the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.80,1:06:58.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為自己曾向楚門拋眉弄眼
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.80,1:06:58.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You think because you batted your eyes at Truman once...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.80,1:07:04.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,打情罵俏... 曾和他一起出鏡幾分鐘\N打情罵俏 曾和他一起出鏡幾分鐘
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.80,1:07:04.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Flirted with him...Stole a few minutes of air time with him...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.50,1:07:07.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,賣弄過自己和自己的政見
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.50,1:07:07.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,to thrust yourself and your politics into the limelight...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.60,1:07:08.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,就以為瞭解他?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.60,1:07:08.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That you know him?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.00,1:07:11.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,知道什麼才適合他?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.00,1:07:11.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That you know what's right for him?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.40,1:07:13.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,有資格去評論他?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.40,1:07:13.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You really think you're in a position to judge him?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.60,1:07:15.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼權力
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.60,1:07:15.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,What right do you have to take a baby
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.80,1:07:19.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,把一個人的一生  塑造成鬧劇
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.80,1:07:19.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And turn his life into some kind of mockery?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.60,1:07:21.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你一點也不覺得內疚?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.60,1:07:21.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't you ever feel guilty?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.40,1:07:27.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我為楚門提供一個正常的人生
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.40,1:07:27.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I have given Truman a chance to lead a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.50,1:07:34.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,這個你所住的世界是病態的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.50,1:07:34.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The world...The place you live in...Is the sick place.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.00,1:07:38.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,桃源才是模範的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.00,1:07:38.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Seahaven's the way the world should be.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.30,1:07:39.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是演員  是囚犯
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.30,1:07:39.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He's not a performer. He's a prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.80,1:07:42.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,任由你擺佈
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.80,1:07:42.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,look at him! Look at what you've done to him!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.30,1:07:43.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他隨時可以走
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.30,1:07:43.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He can leave at any time.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.00,1:07:46.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,假如他稍有野心
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.00,1:07:46.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,If his was more than just a vague ambition,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.50,1:07:50.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,假如他下定決心要查出真相
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.50,1:07:50.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,If he was absolutely determined to discover the truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.40,1:07:53.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們無法阻止他
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.40,1:07:53.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,There's no way we could prevent him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.90,1:07:59.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你不安  其實另有原因
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.90,1:07:59.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I think what distresses you really caller
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.70,1:08:05.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,就是楚門甘願坐你所謂的監獄
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.70,1:08:05.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,is that ultimately...Truman prefers his cell, as you call it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.00,1:08:07.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你錯了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.00,1:08:07.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That's where you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.00,1:08:11.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,大錯特錯  他會證明你是錯的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.00,1:08:11.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're so wrong, and he'll prove you wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.70,1:08:15.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,觀眾甚少有惡評
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.70,1:08:15.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, aside from The heated comments of a very vocal minority
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.80,1:08:18.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,絕大部分都說它有益世道人心
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.80,1:08:18.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's been an overwhelmingly positive experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.50,1:08:21.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,對楚門 對觀眾  都有裨益
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.50,1:08:21.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes. for Truman and for the viewing public.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.10,1:08:23.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,克裡斯多夫  萬分感謝
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.10,1:08:23.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, Christof, I can't thank you enough
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.80,1:08:25.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你百忙中接受訪問
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.80,1:08:25.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,for giving so generously of your time tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.60,1:08:28.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,現在危機已成過去
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.60,1:08:28.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I think it's safe to say now that this crisis is behind us
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.60,1:08:30.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門恢復了常態
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.60,1:08:30.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And Truman is back to his old self,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.60,1:08:33.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,節目會不會有新發展?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.60,1:08:33.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,We can look forward to some exciting new developments?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.10,1:08:35.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,未來的大事是
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.10,1:08:35.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, Mike, the big news
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.10,1:08:38.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,在下一集  美露會離開楚門
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.10,1:08:38.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that Meryl will be leaving Truman in an upcoming episode
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.90,1:08:41.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門將會有第二春
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.90,1:08:41.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,And a new romantic interest will be introduced.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.00,1:08:44.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我決定將性交過程
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.00,1:08:44.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Aha. I'm determined television's first on-air conception
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.80,1:08:46.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,首次在電視上直播
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.80,1:08:46.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,will still take place.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.00,1:08:49.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,電視廣播即將出現新的里程碑
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.00,1:08:49.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, another television milestone straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.80,1:08:51.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已率先為大家透露
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.80,1:08:51.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You heard it here first.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.60,1:08:53.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.60,1:08:53.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It has been a singular honor and pleasure, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.10,1:08:56.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 克裡斯多夫 - 謝謝你  米高
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.10,1:08:56.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Christof  - Thank you. Thank you, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.80,1:10:16.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 西文 - 什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.80,1:10:16.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Hey, Simeon. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.20,1:10:22.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他是不是看著我們?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.20,1:10:22.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Is he looking at us?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.10,1:10:24.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了  難道他看出了破綻?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.10,1:10:24.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Jesus, do you think he knows?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.50,1:10:27.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你好?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.50,1:10:27.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.90,1:10:29.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我要通知克裡斯多夫
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.90,1:10:29.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Better call Christof.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.30,1:10:31.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,報告  畢少校
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.30,1:10:31.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello? Come in, Major Burbank.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.70,1:10:52.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他故態復萌 - 天啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.70,1:10:52.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- He's back to his old self. - Thank god.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.00,1:11:02.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,好怪的貓
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.00,1:11:02.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That's an unusual cat, my man.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.30,1:11:10.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,謹此把本星球命名為...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.30,1:11:10.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I hereby...Proclaim this planet...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.00,1:11:18.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,畢星系楚門星
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.00,1:11:18.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Trumania of the Burbank Galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.90,1:11:22.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他要出去? - 走廊鏡頭準備
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.90,1:11:22.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Is he going? - Hallway camera.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.70,1:11:25.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,免費表演一次
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.70,1:11:25.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That one's for free.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.90,1:11:28.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,跟貼  他行動有點快
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.90,1:11:28.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Keep up with him. He'll move fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.50,1:11:30.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,全部攝影機準備
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.50,1:11:30.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Stand by, all house cameras.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.70,1:11:35.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,早安!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.70,1:11:35.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.10,1:11:36.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,假如再碰不見你...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.10,1:11:36.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Morning. In case I don't see you...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.80,1:11:39.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你早 午 晚都安
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.80,1:11:39.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, good evening, and good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.00,1:11:44.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 午安 - 早安
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.00,1:11:44.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Good afternoon - Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.30,1:11:47.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,...午安 晚安
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.30,1:11:47.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,...evening, and good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.60,1:11:49.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 早安  楚門 - 早安  史賓沙
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.60,1:11:49.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Morning. - Morning, spencer.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.80,1:11:52.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你好嗎? - 讓我檢查一下
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.80,1:11:52.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- How's it going? - Hmm, let me check.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.00,1:11:54.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,主要功能健全
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.00,1:11:54.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Vital signs are good.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.00,1:11:57.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,阿冥!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.00,1:11:57.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Whoa, Pluto! Whoop!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.80,1:12:01.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 早安  楚門 - 原來是你們
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.80,1:12:01.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- Good morning, Truman - Oh, look who's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.60,1:12:04.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 今天天氣很好 - 天天都這樣好
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.60,1:12:04.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Beautiful day, isn't it? Every single day.
