Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.50,1:26:42.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他連浸死也不怕
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.50,1:26:42.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He's gonna drown, and he doesn't even care.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.10,1:26:44.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,吹翻他!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.10,1:26:44.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Do it. No. Do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.10,1:27:40.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.10,1:27:40.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.40,1:30:00.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.40,1:30:00.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.40,1:30:03.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.40,1:30:03.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.30,1:31:52.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟他談談
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.30,1:31:52.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.30,1:32:00.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,(出口)
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.70,1:32:13.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.70,1:32:13.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Truman.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.80,1:32:15.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以說話
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.80,1:32:15.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You can speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.20,1:32:19.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽得到你
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.20,1:32:19.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.20,1:32:25.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.20,1:32:25.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.50,1:32:26.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我是創造者
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.50,1:32:26.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I am the creator of a television show
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.60,1:32:31.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,創造了一個 受萬眾歡迎的電視節目
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.60,1:32:31.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That gives hope and joy and inspiration to millions.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.90,1:32:37.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我是誰?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.90,1:32:37.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Then who am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.80,1:32:39.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是那個節目的明星
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.80,1:32:39.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're the star.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.20,1:32:46.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都是假的?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.20,1:32:46.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Was nothing real?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.00,1:32:49.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你是真的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.00,1:32:49.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You were real.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.10,1:32:52.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才有那麼多人看你
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.10,1:32:52.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That's what made you so good to watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.80,1:32:53.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我勸告
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.80,1:32:53.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Truman.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.30,1:32:56.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,外面的世界...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.30,1:32:56.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,There's no more truth out there...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.70,1:33:00.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我給你的世界一樣的虛假
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.70,1:33:00.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,than there is in the world I created for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.20,1:33:03.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,有一樣的謊言
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.20,1:33:03.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The same lies.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.50,1:33:06.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,一樣的欺詐
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.50,1:33:06.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The same deceit.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.90,1:33:09.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,但在我的世界...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.90,1:33:09.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,But in my world...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.30,1:33:13.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼也不用怕
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.30,1:33:13.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You have nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.30,1:33:18.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我比你更清楚你自己
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.30,1:33:18.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I know you better than you know yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.70,1:33:20.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你無法在我腦內裝攝影機
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.70,1:33:20.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You never had a camera in my head.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.10,1:33:23.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你害怕
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.10,1:33:23.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.40,1:33:26.80,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你不能走
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.40,1:33:26.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why you can't leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.90,1:33:35.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,楚門  不要緊  我明白
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.90,1:33:35.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,It's Ok, Truman. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.20,1:33:39.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,我看了你的一生
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.20,1:33:39.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I have been watching you your whole life.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.40,1:33:45.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你出生時  我在看你
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.40,1:33:45.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I was watching when you were born.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.30,1:33:50.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你學走路時  我在看你
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.30,1:33:50.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I was watching when you took your first step.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.10,1:33:56.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你入學  我在看你
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.10,1:33:56.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,I watched you on your first day of school.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.50,1:34:01.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,還有你掉第一顆牙齒那一幕
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.50,1:34:01.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The episode when you lost your first tooth.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.40,1:34:07.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能離開  楚門
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.40,1:34:07.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You can't leave, Truman.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.90,1:34:10.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝  求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.90,1:34:10.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Please, god.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.30,1:34:12.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你屬於這裡...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.30,1:34:12.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You belong here...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.10,1:34:14.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以走出去
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.10,1:34:14.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.00,1:34:16.90,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.00,1:34:16.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.70,1:34:20.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.70,1:34:20.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.50,1:34:23.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,說句話
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.50,1:34:23.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.00,1:34:31.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,你他媽的說句話! 你上了電視了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.00,1:34:31.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, say something, goddamn it. You're on television.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.70,1:34:33.70,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,正在向全世界直播
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.70,1:34:33.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,You're live to the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.20,1:34:52.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,假如再碰不見你...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.20,1:34:52.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,In case I don't see you...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.10,1:34:56.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你早 午 晚都安
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.10,1:34:56.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, good evening, and good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.20,1:35:01.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,耶 
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.20,1:35:01.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.70,1:35:26.30,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,歐耶!歐耶! 
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.70,1:35:26.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.40,1:35:31.50,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他做到了 他做到了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.40,1:35:31.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He did it. He did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.70,1:35:34.00,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他做到了! 他做到了!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.70,1:35:34.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He did it! He did it!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.50,1:35:39.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,他走脫了! 走吧! 楚門!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.50,1:35:39.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,He made it! Yeah! All right, Truman!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.50,1:35:50.10,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,停播 
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.50,1:35:50.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Cease transmission.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.20,1:35:51.60,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,停播 
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.20,1:35:51.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Ceasing transmission.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.30,1:35:57.40,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 要多一片嗎? - 不要了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.30,1:35:57.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- You want another slice? - No. I'm Ok.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.60,1:36:01.20,CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,- 還有什麼節目? - 看看還有什麼 - 還有什麼節目? - 看看還有什麼 電視預告尼?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.60,1:36:01.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,,- What else is on? - Let's see what else is on. Where's the TV guide?

